    "name": "Nano!",
    "profile": "Juan Manuel Abrigo also known as Nano!, was born in 1982 in Argentina. When he was 14 years old, started to play the guitar and listen a big number of discs. Some years then, he discovered the computer world and the way of lisen and make music. In 2004, he saw with good face the idea of be a dj, and started to play in the most important clubs and bars of the city. Today, he is a software developer, dj and producer. His musical likes go by a great quantity of styles, especially the minimalistic sounds. In his dj sets he tries to create a good atmosphere whit minimal, tech house and the sounds of future.",
